  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed extension, by reason of its size, depth, and location is an inappropriate, unsympathetic, and disproportionate addition to the property that would adversely affect the character and appearance of the host building and the wider area, contrary to policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020), policy D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021) and the advice in the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009). &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of the additional depth and height along the boundary, would have a tunnelling and overbearing impact that would further reduce the outlook of the adjoining occupiers. As such the proposal fails to meet the requirements of policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character), and policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and the advice in the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
